description: RNA-seq of human testis tissue. The second technical replicate was performed in May 2015 and was not part of the original Lin et al. 2014 publication (PMID:25413365).
RNA-seq of human testis tissue. The second technical replicate was performed in May 2015 and was not part of the original Lin et al. 2014 publication (PMID:25413365).

The libraries contained in this experiment come from the cytoplasmic fraction of independent growths of the human embryonic stem cell line H1-hESC. They are stranded PE76 Illumina GAIIx RNA-Seq libraries from rRNA-depleted Poly-A+ RNA > 200 nucleotides in size.
